204
00:11:23,980 --> 00:11:28,500
♪Walk the mountains, asking directions
,divining fortune or misfortune♪

205
00:11:28,660 --> 00:11:33,140
♪Gazing afar, like a fleeting glimpse
of a youthful elegance♪

206
00:11:33,260 --> 00:11:37,700
♪Advance or retreat, even in despair,
one should not yield♪

207
00:11:37,820 --> 00:11:39,700
♪Ride away, a lone figure
through countless waves♪

208
