♪Looking back at the road traveled♪

219
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:20,740
♪By your side,
the passing of time is fearless♪

220
00:12:29,700 --> 00:12:34,340
♪Facing crossroads, the wind whispers
a kiss without asking love or hate♪

221
00:12:34,540 --> 00:12:36,440
♪A sorrowful song plays,
a healer's skillful touch♪

222
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:39,180
♪Never forgetting the word "compassion"♪

223
