♪That youth,
with a few loyal friends by his side♪

224
00:12:43,740 --> 00:12:45,540
♪Carrying liquor,
the heart still burns hot♪

225
00:12:45,780 --> 00:12:48,340
♪The world bears witness
to my sincerity♪

226
